Agnes Osazuwa (onye amuru na 26 June 1989 na Benin City, Edo) bu nwanyi egwuregwu n'asọmpi maka Naịjirịa mba ụwa niile
Osazuwa nọchitere anya Naịjirịa na 2008 Summer Olympics na Beijing na asọmpi ọsọ nke 4x100 yana Gloria Kemasuode, Oludamola Osayomi and Ene Franca Idoko
Ha gbara nke anọ n'azụ Belgium, Great Britain na Brazil
Oge ha nke 43.43 sekọnd bụ oge kachasị mma na-erughị eru na oge nke isii n'asompi ahu nke obodo iri na isii sonyere
Oge ahụ ka ha jiri gaa ọsọ ikpeazu n'asompi ahụ mana ha jiri Halimat Ismaila dochie Osazuwa
Oge nke a ka ha ji 43.04 sekond gbaa nke atọ na merie ọla nchara
